snippet.title: Xprite Burst Series 12V COB LED Amber Roof Top Emergency Hazard
snippet.description:
great light for under $60.00 
Amazon link:  https://www.amazon.ca/gp/product/B078HNXQX3/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_image_o06_s01?ie=UTF8&psc=1

FEATURES - Xprite High Intensity LED Safety Caution Flash Strobe Lights Bar are great for emergency construction vehicle, postal service, safety warning etc. COB LEDs are Multiple LED Mhips Bonded Together to form a Single Module. Technology Results in a Greatly Increased Lumen Output. Enhanced Optical LEDs to Magnify Brightness.
PATTERN - Easy on/off power.2nd switch to simply change over 19 kinds of the different strobe / flashing patterns, great for undercover or to use when needed. Patterns include Rotating, Flashing, Alternating Between Left and Right Side, etc.Up to 50,000 hours life.
HIGH QUALITY - Made of High Quality Transparent PC Materials, Crystal Clear for Maximum Brightness, Anti-impact, Scratch Resistant. Designed to Withstand Harsh Weather Conditions. Waterproof Rate - IP67.
DIMENSIONS - Cable: 11.1" (length) x 2.1" (height) x 6.5" (depth); Power Wire: 10 FT High-Quality Non-Stretchable (straight),Newest Straight Cable Will Give you the Entire 10 FT with NO Issues.
EASY INSTALLATION - This strobe light LED is specifically designed to work on all vehicles with a 12V cigarrette plug and magnetized bottom to place on any metal exterior. 2 Magnetic pods (12 Powerful Magnets ) with protective rubber feet.
